These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, musical, animation
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, train
1. the person watching epic movies is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | animation | musical    |
| Transport     | quad-bike    | train       | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, architect, manager
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, tennis, soccer
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the manager is on the left of the security-guard##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left or far right##3
4. the architect is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | manager | security-guard | architect  |
| Sport   | surfing  | tennis  | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, architect, writer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, dubstep, country
1. the fan of dubstep is on the far left or far right##3
2. the bartender is on the far right##1
3. the architect is the fan of country##1
4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job           | writer | architect | bartender |
| Music-Genre   | rock        | country    | dubstep        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, writing, magic-tricks
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, ferret, lizard
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
3. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | writing | filmmaking |
| Pet     | ferret  | hedgehog    | lizard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, superhero, crime
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching superhero movies and the person driving the scooter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | documentary | crime |
| Transport     | motorbike   | jet-ski   | scooter   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks, collecting
The people have 3 different jobs:  teacher, doctor, writer
1. the writer is on the left of the teacher##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Hobby   | collecting | fishing | magic-tricks      |
| Job     | doctor  | writer | teacher |

