.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, trance, soul
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, polish, indian
1. the fan of soul is on the right of the polish##1
2. the indian is on the left of the fan of indie##1
3. the indian is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | soul    | indie       |
| Nationality   | polish | indian | brazilian |

