.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, water, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: peach, raspberry, pear
1. the person drinking juice is the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating raspberry is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk        | water  | juice   |
| Food       | pear | raspberry | peach |

