2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the journalist##1
3. the bartender is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the musician is on the left or right of the bartender##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2       |       3        |
| Beverage   | coffee | juice         | tea          |
| Job        | journalist | musician | bartender |

