.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, coffee
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, british, turkish
1. the chinese is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the british is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the chinese is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate    | coffee    | iced-tea  |
| Nationality   | british | chinese | turkish |

