.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, thai, british
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard, pony
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
2. the british is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the hedgehog##2
4. the owner of the hedgehog is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | spanish | british | thai |
| Pet           | lizard    | pony    | hedgehog       |

