.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, sudoku, writing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, rugby, basketball
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
3. the person who's sport is basketball is the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Hobby   | writing    | skydiving   | sudoku |
| Sport   | rugby | basketball | volleyball |

