.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-16::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, time-travel, thriller
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, house, r&b
1. the fan of house is in the middle##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is between the fan of r&b and the fan of gospel##2
3. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
4. the fan of r&b is the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | thriller | mystery |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | house  | r&b    |

